{"tid":2267573,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國女諧星朴智宣與母親 今日驚傳住宅內雙雙身亡","createTime":"2020-11-02T07:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T08:55:58.000Z","uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c7cd7d3f47f6b9561b755e76bf1fc0983734d1","tid":2267573,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"韓國女諧星朴智宣今日驚傳身亡，終年35歲。<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒報道，朴智宣跟母親的遺體於今日下午被發現倒卧在麻浦區的住宅內。據知朴智宣的爸爸因為聯絡不到她而覺得奇怪，報警後和警方一起破門而入，發現母女倆已死亡，警方正在調查死亡原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5244/5244109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5244%2F5244109.jpg&h=55e1d63b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7f191a8b6c7dbe2a040478045ac290827e2c2e7","tid":2267573,"uid":213446,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"2020 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60da874d4a2b7263224cadcd3058d976cb46a61","tid":2267573,"uid":219583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"仲以為係朴智星留左長毛 幾似樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw rip"},{"pid":"d2a6972d3c8434affd276e746178a3bfc3b489e5","tid":2267573,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e81824afc3df1a79eb73f8f823ede0926c08bed","tid":2267573,"uid":124310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:53:51.000Z","msg":"2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf204ca5bb3a17612741740e46fd6f568a558826","